<pb n="0001a" id="T01.0001.0001a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0001a01" ed="T"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/><head type="no">No. 1</head>
<lb n="0001a02" ed="T"/><div1 type="xu"><mulu level="1" label="序" type="序"/><note n="0001001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">此序依宋元明三本&M062443;依&M062438;載&M062425;</note><foreign n="0001009" resp="Taisho" lang="san" place="foot">1. Nid&amacron;na.</foreign><head><title>長阿含經</title>序</head>
<lb n="0001a03" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0001a04" ed="T"/><byline type="Author"><note n="0001002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔長安〕－【宋】</note><app n="0001002"><lem wit="【大】">長安</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">&Amacron;</rdg></app>釋僧肇<note n="0001003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔述〕－【宋】</note><app n="0001003"><lem wit="【大】">述</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">&CB00006;</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="0001a05" ed="T"/><p id="pT01p0001a0501">夫宗極絕於稱謂。賢聖以之沖默。玄旨非言
<lb n="0001a06" ed="T"/>不傳。釋迦所以致教。是以如來出世。大教
<lb n="0001a07" ed="T"/>有三。約身口。則防之以禁律。明善惡。則導之
<lb n="0001a08" ed="T"/>以契經。演幽微。則<note n="0001004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">辨＝辯【宋】＊</note><app n="0001004"><lem wit="【CBETA】">辨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【大】">辯</rdg></app>之以法相。然則三藏
<lb n="0001a09" ed="T"/>之作也。本於殊應。&Amacron;會之有宗。則異途同趣矣。</p>
</div1>
